OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA warm sunny
OL,6,Fevening then a dry and mainly clear
OL,7,Fnight, though low cloud and mist on
OL,8,Fnorth coast may drift down the Bann
OL,9,FValley.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FA dry and bright day with
OL,12,Fvariable cloud and sunny spells and
OL,13,Ffeeling very warm or hot. Low cloud
OL,14,Fand mist near the north coast slowly
OL,15,Fburning off.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA dry
OL,18,Fweekend with long bright or sunny
OL,19,Fspells but the mornings starting
OL,20,Fcloudy. Monday dry and sunny. Very
OL,21,Fwarm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
